See ChangeLog for more.

* 1.3.8

Remove history option gl-erase.  Constant gl-erase returns now
gl-all.

Replace bool with int.

Add config and build tool scripts for scons.  It's a replacement
for autoconfig tools.

Remove command line option -h.

New global function fth_xt_call and fth_xt_apply added.

New global function fth_regexp_var_ref added.

Global variable *clm-output-device* removed from
examples/site-lib/clm.fs.
